    public class ResourceBundleResolver
extends DummyTransformResolver
    ResourceBundle resolver. Unlike ResourceBundleLambda this resolver is not limited to String-based values. However keep in mind that resource bundle keys cannot contain dots.
    Author:
    Martin Kouba
    See Also:
    ResourceBundle, ResourceBundleLambda, ResourceBundleHelper
